{"tid":1643814,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【齊來送1.7億比誠哥】令政府由收稅變支出的簡單方法","createTime":"2019-10-10T10:00:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T09:36:22.000Z","uid":288881,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f4e8fafcb919f0a4edf8a24d8e4e2e495ca7501b","tid":1643814,"uid":288881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T10:00:16.000Z","msg":"首先感謝 <strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">勇武港女</span></strong> 諗出「【交佢老母】合法簡易交差餉/水費/公屋租金/稅方法 PPS懶人包」呢條絕世好橋，詳情睇　<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1642316/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1642316/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家唔一定等到綠色信封先開始，今日已經可以開始實行大計<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係PPS點set <strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">勇武港女</span></strong> 已經圖文並茂，小妹唔多講</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QiGs1zz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQiGs1zz.jpg&h=9acb091d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家懶惰的可以月尾set哂下個月28/31日的自動繳款 (誠哥點解你唔整個常行指示呀???)<br />\n小妹朋友計左條數 每個月阻你5分鐘 每日1蚊咁交 誠哥就每人每日2蚊咁袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6gTK3NO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6gTK3NO.jpg&h=da17a9eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">遊行都有2百萬人 禁幾粒制唔係唔禁呀<br />\n只要有50萬人幫手 去到3月底誠哥就賺到<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.72億</span></span></strong>嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\nbtw, 記得3月31日交哂尾數再比多1蚊港共, 根據說明，稅局就要做張支票退比你，<br />\n如果人多既話有排佢做，達到不合作運動效果<br />\n而且完全合法，就算佢搬龍門，都無得收多你，<br />\n下期交小番一蚊唔會益到班狗官 (By あおつき <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1426403/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1426403/page/1</a>)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n香港人，反抗</span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a7ed382e81f3f5bb3cba1f2de0d9dfe5737c2229","tid":1643814,"uid":66822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T10:01:00.000Z","msg":"星期五中環快閃 撐被捕保安<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FoM1jNJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFoM1jNJ.jpg&h=eaa6b73f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7onWS7K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7onWS7K.jpg&h=4e446c9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39e538cecca96b6658159ac6755b6080b569fa4c","tid":1643814,"uid":288881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T10:01:38.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到，希望大家多多支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4783118b39bad8e3d974dc23a20dc7807b4e5b7f","tid":1643814,"uid":288881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T10:06:49.000Z","msg":"推下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15888c88ccc128d38db9895f41b46d9e6d8b13ec","tid":1643814,"uid":288881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T10:13:07.000Z","msg":"人來呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a66026f00390d699b807589bc1a73e724253ec0","tid":1643814,"uid":38819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T10:23:48.000Z","msg":"唔係每一期稅單都唔同編號？<br />\n點樣set定？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"513b2fd7a66f99a01beff3971b49aa4d2bb6411f","tid":1643814,"uid":288881,"like"